#. [message]: id=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:597
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re about to be healed by $hp_difference hitpoints, but it’s time to "
"summon some help against that quintain."
